clause_text: dated……………………………). The work has been completed to my best satisfaction the workmanship and all the materials (type and grade) have been used strictly in accordance with general and detailed specifications. No provisions of the Act or Development Control Regulations or no requisitions made, conditions prescribed or orders issued thereunder have been transgressed in the course of the work. I am enclosing three copies of the completion plans, one of which is cloth mounted. The building is fit for occupancy for which it has been erected/re- erected or altered, constructed and enlarged.
